#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
typedef long long int ll;
const int SIZE = 2e5+5;
ll arr[SIZE];
ll ff,ss;
int n;
int main(int argc,char* argv[]){
    scanf("%d",&n);
    ff = ss = 0LL;
    for(int i = 0;i<n;i++){
            scanf("%lld",&arr[i]);
     if(arr[i]>ff)
        ss = ff,ff = arr[i];
     else if(arr[i]==ff)
        ss = ff;
     else if(arr[i]>ss)
        ss = arr[i];
    }
    printf("%lld %lld\n",ff,ss);
    return 0;
}
